### React Native SQLite-2 Usage with RxDB

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/rx-storage-sqlite.md

This snippet provides an alternative for React Native projects, demonstrating RxDB integration with the 'react-native-sqlite-2' library. It uses `getSQLiteBasicsWebSQL` with `SQLite.openDatabase` to configure the storage.

```typescript
import {
    getRxStorageSQLite,
    getSQLiteBasicsWebSQL
} from 'rxdb-premium/plugins/storage-sqlite';
import SQLite from 'react-native-sqlite-2';
const storage = getRxStorageSQLite({
  sqliteBasics: getSQLiteBasicsWebSQL(SQLite.openDatabase)
});
```

